At first, I was nervous about opening up our home and office, but I quickly realised I was in great hands. I’m now thrilled and excited to share these images of our beloved spaces presented beautifully by @archdigestindia / @archdigest on their September-October Style issue which will be on stands next week! It was a pleasure working with this incredible team! 

A huge thank you to @nikhilmansata @rooshadshroff @chandnimodha_ @amritajhaveriart @lilyfro @isabelledubern @claravvvv for holding my hand through this.
